 state. that kind of leadership skill i think is exactly what america needs right now." </p><p><em>to watch governor (candidate last), please see:</em> <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vdfazqg9lcq">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vdfazqg9lcq</a></p></span>



